data.description: Beautiful 3-bedromm 2-bathroom home with an additional detached 650 sq. ft. building that was built with permits. It can be used for storage or built out to be in law quarters.  This home has a large backyard with fruit trees and a covered terrace perfect for entertaining and family gatherings. Ample space for boat or RV. Close to shops and restaurants and just a few blocks from the turnpike.
